divs: sighting detailsat st. marks wildlife refuge facing the gulf \bay noticed airplane moving high rate of speed . looked around and then looked almost straight up and noticed the triangle . took a pic of it , took pic of aircraft flying at high speed , looked back at triangle it was gone . i am sending the high def pic so when you enlarge it you will see what im talking about . i use olympus e500 8 megpix with zuiko 70-300 zoom . i have gone back saturday and sunday and havent seen it anymore .
Summary: UFO seen at St. Marks Wildlife Refuge above the bay.
